Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DIALOGUE
Dialogue: 3,0:00:04.31,0:00:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to avoid being late to the date she finally agreed to,
Dialogue: 3,0:00:08.65,0:00:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran over to the meeting spot as early as I could that day.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:14.24,0:00:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it was because it was Christmas?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:16.74,0:00:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place was bustling with more couples than usual.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:19.74,0:00:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for someone just like\Neveryone else, and it made me happy.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:31.24,0:00:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.07,0:00:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I got the time and place right...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:39.93,0:00:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Christmas Eve, two years ago.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:42.88,0:00:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1150)}She never showed up to the date.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:37.34,0:02:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 3,0:02:44.99,0:02:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Nii-nii still isn't up yet?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:54.73,0:02:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't she come to our date two years ago?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:59.50,0:03:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know why.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:02.35,0:03:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, I've...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-nii!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you shut yourself in the closet again?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:10.47,0:03:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be late for school if you don't get up now!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-nii!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:18.53,0:03:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, I still want to sleep.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:21.19,0:03:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold and I don't wanna get out yet.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you needed to do was turn the heater on...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:27.41,0:03:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if Nii-nii won't come out, I'll go in instead!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:31.23,0:03:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I saw your closet planetarium too.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.61,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it, don't come in!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a masterpiece I made for my own private enjoyment!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:39.72,0:03:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masterpiece?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just drew it with a highlighter!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shut up!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:44.38,0:03:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in too!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll come out.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:55.10,0:03:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Miya?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-nii, you dummy!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-nii, it's been so long since we walked to school together.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:03.95,0:04:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:04.76,0:04:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Nii-nii, you usually go ahead and leave me behind.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you keep taking your time, Miya.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:10.89,0:04:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we're not at home now, so don't call me "Nii-nii".
Dialogue: 3,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:15.41,0:04:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.  Sorry!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:18.02,0:04:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you the one who asked not to be so clingy at school?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:22.54,0:04:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.  Onii-chan, see you later!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:25.24,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:26.08,0:04:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:27.80,0:04:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miya-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's Miya's friend.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walking to school with a hot chick.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing hotter than that in the morning.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really blows away the winter cold, eh, Tachibana?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:38.15,0:04:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know you?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  This again?  This trick again?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:41.37,0:04:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall having a friend who'd\Ntease me like that knowing she is my sister.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no fun.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:47.82,0:04:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was going to share something new with you too...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the photo album you were talking about?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:53.18,0:04:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought it with me for the sake of my best friend,
Dialogue: 3,0:04:56.30,0:04:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like this friendship is one-sided.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!  Now that I take a closer look,\Naren't you the second son of a sushi chef,
Dialogue: 3,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my best friend who's been in my class\Nsince elementary school, Umehara Masayoshi?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:05.88,0:05:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You change personalities pretty quickly.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:11.51,0:05:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you're still my best friend, Tachibana Junichi.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:14.07,0:05:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I was just waiting for that reaction.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how was it?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now now, no need to get that excited.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was awesome.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does sound pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend it to you, don't worry.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:39.89,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't {\i1}stain{\i0\fscx125} {\r}my precious book, though.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I won't!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding, man.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:47.16,0:05:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:48.19,0:05:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she Morishima-senpai?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:52.70,0:05:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,560)}Oh come on, Hibiki!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so beautiful, it's surreal.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:58.85,0:06:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She makes the photo album look dull.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:04.69,0:06:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morishima-senpai is beautiful, as always.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:09.28,0:06:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She also has a lot of fans at our school.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:13.44,0:06:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, she recently rejected some guy in our class.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, let's hurry or we'll be late.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:21.83,0:06:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting anything if we're late because of this!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:25.44,0:06:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:32.18,0:06:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's Founder's Festival is fast approaching.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:35.65,0:06:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, we need to decide on\Ncommittee members from this class.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any volunteers?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:43.68,0:06:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:45.09,0:06:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If no one wants to do it, I will.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayatsuji-san?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:50.09,0:06:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already working as the class representative.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:53.11,0:06:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want another position?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:55.29,0:06:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  I don't really have much work left as\Nclass representative now that it's November.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:59.85,0:07:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it's only a short while until the\NFounder's Festival, which is around Christmas.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:03.89,0:07:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, please do your best.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:06.26,0:07:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:06.84,0:07:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we're halfway through November...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:10.35,0:07:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayatsuji-san always does the things no one else wants to do.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really hardworking.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sup, boss.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:32.23,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have lunch.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:33.55,0:07:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we buy some bread today?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right there!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of having bread today too.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna tag along then, Tanamachi?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fun if we all go together.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:49.82,0:07:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a game of rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:52.25,0:07:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever loses has to buy bread for all three of us.  What do you think?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:59.39,0:08:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:06.53,0:08:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Yakisoba bread and a chocolate cornet!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:09.04,0:08:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a pork sandwich and a red bean paste bun.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:11.77,0:08:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this looks bad.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be a freshman.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:23.03,0:08:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a trick to buying bread at times like this.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here to buy bread, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a milk and one of the sweet breads...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:44.78,0:08:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.  Milk and something sweet.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:49.68,0:08:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just chose whatever.  You okay with that?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:52.35,0:08:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:56.32,0:08:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How much?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the price?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was 360 yen.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:04.38,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best next time.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl just then...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:09.83,0:09:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was all red and flustered.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:12.40,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have offered to help.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.  I'd better pick them all up...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there with the big appetite!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morishima-senpai.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:34.09,0:09:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  Have we met before?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:37.90,0:09:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped it, big appetite-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:42.27,0:09:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:52.14,0:09:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have adorable eyes.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:55.67,0:09:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did we meet somewhere before?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:00.44,0:10:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  That makes sense.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:04.16,0:10:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I usually remember people I've met before.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:08.11,0:10:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, weren't you the guy who bought bread for that freshman?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.  You're really nice.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.  Make sure you don't fall over again!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:26.79,0:10:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to talk with Morishima-senpai...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:31.59,0:10:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still smell her wonderful scent.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rihoko.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:46.24,0:10:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:46.90,0:10:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to eat all of that?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd probably be able to finish all of this yourself though, Rihoko.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:57.96,0:11:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  I definitely can't eat that much.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:04.57,0:11:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so slow I thought I was gonna die of hunger!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what were you doing?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of things happened.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disturb you while you're eating,
Dialogue: 3,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:18.75,0:11:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayatsuji-san, what is it?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:20.91,0:11:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei asked me to collect\Neveryone's guidance papers by today,
Dialogue: 3,0:11:26.94,0:11:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're the only one who hasn't turned one in yet, Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you turn it in before you leave today?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I forgot about it.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn it in later.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:36.62,0:11:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'd appreciate it.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn it in to the teacher.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you had to wait for me.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:04.64,0:12:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was just wondering where Umehara went.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:08.03,0:12:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His bag is still at his desk, so I don't think he went home yet.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:12.55,0:12:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Umehara-kun,\Nhe said something about going to the library.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:16.64,0:12:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:17.38,0:12:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't paid me back yet for the bread earlier,\Nso I need to bug him about that.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?  You should definitely talk to him about that.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Well, I'll go look in the library.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:28.22,0:12:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also need to get a good look at his new photo album!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morishima-senpai?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:49.00,0:12:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  Aren't you the one with the big appetite from lunchtime?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice timing!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:55.43,0:12:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:57.47,0:13:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got impatient looking around for someone...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:00.22,0:13:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:01.88,0:13:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't looking where I was going either.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you're doing me a big favor by carrying those books.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay, though?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:08.69,0:13:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you looking for someone?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:10.34,0:13:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:11.88,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had some business with him, but it can wait.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:15.94,0:13:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there aren't many things more important than carrying stuff for Morishima-senpai.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:22.88,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiki-chan!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Haruka?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:28.46,0:13:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They actually had all these\Nphoto books of cute dogs at the library!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:32.42,0:13:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Borrowing them wasn't that bad,\Nbut carrying them around is tough.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I got him to help.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Haruka has troubled you.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was free too.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:51.11,0:13:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka, go ahead and thank him properly.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:53.99,0:13:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, uh...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:58.02,0:14:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I still don't know your name.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:01.79,0:14:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:03.28,0:14:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm T-Tachibana Junichi from Class 2-A.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Tachibana Junichi-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:10.77,0:14:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:13.22,0:14:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even know his name, and yet you made him carry all this, Haruka?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:18.99,0:14:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not have known his name,\Nbut I knew I could count on Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:25.34,0:14:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Tachibana-kun's really nice.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Tachibana!  Check this out!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They actually kept photo book treasures like these hidden away at the library!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to get them right after I heard about them.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the former students probably left it behi{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:14:46.97,0:14:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:49.74,0:14:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll try again.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Try what again?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those feelings I lost two years ago...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:58.53,0:15:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to find them again.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:01.87,0:15:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:03.33,0:15:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morishima-senpai.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:04.97,0:15:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the school idol and probably unreachable,
Dialogue: 3,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.06,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think I'm falling for her.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:11.83,0:15:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, your face is all red!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a cold?  Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:26.53,0:15:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years ago on Christmas, my heart was broken.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:31.41,0:15:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became afraid of having to go through that again.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:36.03,0:15:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this year I'll definitely have a blessed Christmas!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:39.61,0:15:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, Morishima-senpai is way out of my league.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:43.54,0:15:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I haven't seen her since that incident at the library.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no way things would go that smoothly.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me play too!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morishima-senpai?!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morishima-senpai?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:06.06,0:16:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Morishima-senpai?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:09.26,0:16:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I was thinking there were a bunch of kids\Nplaying leapfrog, until I saw you with them.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:14.61,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought I'd join in too!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came out of nowhere, so you really surprised me.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:19.75,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be fine with me jumping in, Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's because you're really nice.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I played leapfrog!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:30.23,0:16:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to play it with the boys from my elementary school.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:33.75,0:16:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:36.52,0:16:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miya.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miya, this is Morishima-senpai.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've heard of her.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:44.47,0:16:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, this is my sister, Miya.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:47.94,0:16:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:49.99,0:16:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister's adorable.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's nothing but cheeky.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to switch classrooms for\Nmy afternoon classes, so I'm off.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miya!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:02.26,0:17:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:04.64,0:17:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably hates me now.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miya-chan is so cute though.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like a kitty.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:12.54,0:17:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get closer to her, so we can go shopping and take baths together!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, b-baths?!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:18.77,0:17:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!  It'll be fun!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:24.96,0:17:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morishima-senpai and Miya together in the bath...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:28.23,0:17:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haru-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:29.78,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all I need to do to make my boobs bigger?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but you should do it like this...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:38.04,0:17:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.  You're good, Miya!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:40.15,0:17:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this kinda tickles.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:44.66,0:17:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, I'll have to ask Miya\Nwhy she wasn't very happy later.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:53.22,0:17:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miya!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:55.76,0:17:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:56.99,0:18:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you so rude to Morishima-senpai this lunch break?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:02.02,0:18:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said you were cute and wanted to get closer to you.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:06.78,0:18:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:07.93,0:18:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't {\i1}you{\i0\fscx125} {\r}the one who wants to get closer to her, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:10.40,0:18:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Morishima-senpai is really pretty and has a nice body?!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:14.28,0:18:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, getting all lovestruck?!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:17.15,0:18:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-nii, you dummy!
Dialogue: 3,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Morishima-senpai...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:08.32,0:19:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, take this.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:17.46,0:19:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana-kun...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a disposable hand warmer?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold otherwise.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:23.69,0:19:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:24.66,0:19:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really nice.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking at the water.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The... water?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:37.09,0:19:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:38.51,0:19:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like looking at water.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:41.94,0:19:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sea, the river...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the fountain.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:45.53,0:19:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds nice.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:46.81,0:19:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it suits you somehow, Morishima-senpai.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:51.89,0:19:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Hibiki are probably the only ones who've said that to me.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so nice.  Why, you!
Dialogue: 3,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not it at all.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:01.70,0:20:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you saying you're only this nice towards me?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:05.99,0:20:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:07.38,0:20:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you like me?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:11.18,0:20:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, well...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:17.04,0:20:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:20.97,0:20:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so warm...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:36.81,0:20:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, Morishima-senpai!
Dialogue: 3,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really!
Dialogue: 3,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:49.69,0:20:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:52.30,0:20:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more of a man than I thought, Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:55.49,0:20:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kinda surprised me.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:59.47,0:21:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:02.07,0:21:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:05.78,0:21:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer someone who's reliable and older than me.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:10.34,0:21:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:13.24,0:21:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you, Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and thanks for the hand warmer.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really warm.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:28.03,0:21:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana-kun?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:32.39,0:21:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:33.28,0:21:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I rejected?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did I really confess to her?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:38.14,0:21:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.  That wasn't a confession.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.79,0:21:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go home for now.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:53.02,0:21:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-nii, you're home?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.14,0:21:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some steamed meat buns.  Do you want some?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:05.38,0:22:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:07.50,0:22:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll go in.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:50.99,0:23:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode preview...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:52.61,0:23:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-nii, you're not having any steamed meat buns?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:55.16,0:23:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:55.78,0:23:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 3,0:23:56.61,0:23:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're so good!
Dialogue: 3,0:24:00.97,0:24:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The juices overflowing in your mouth,
Dialogue: 3,0:24:02.51,0:24:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the chewiness and savory taste of the meat...
Dialogue: 3,0:24:07.21,0:24:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Miya.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:08.71,0:24:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem happy.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:10.76,0:24:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: "Approach".
Dialogue: 3,0:24:12.84,0:24:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-nii, the sun will rise again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 3,0:24:15.59,0:24:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, p-please look forward to the next episode.
